@pr4ger: Looks like the decoupler's DragCube was improperly configured. If you open up the Mk2Expansion/parts/Structural/decoupler/part.cfg and replace the DRAG\_CUBE section of the config with:

DRAG\_CUBE  

    {  

        cube = Default, 0.1846,0.5943,1.355, 0.1846,0.5943,1.355, 2.476,0.7572,0.09955, 2.476,0.7572,0.09955, 0.3174,0.7253,0.7, 0.3174,0.7253,0.7, 0,-0.06703,-6.076E-09, 2.5,0.1255,1.5  

    }

it should fix the problem.

